title: Live Event Tomorrow!
dc:creator: Tyler Folkman
content:encoded:
Hey! I'm doing my first LinkedIn Live event tomorrow!

It is going to be a ton of fun and I would love to have you there!

If you're looking to break into the field of data science and would like to better understand AI applications in entertainment

Or

You are sick of hearing so much about AI and want to cut straight to the reality of AI and how you might use it in your company

Then this event is for you!

Come and ask me your best questions! And make sure to RSVP!

RSVP to Live Event

See you tomorrow,

Tyler
